#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Barbarian production site: Independent Fishing Hut
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:37 input:37
#: standard
msgctxt "barbarians_building"
msgid "‘What do you mean, my fish ain’t fresh?!’"
msgstr "\"Vad menar du med att min fisk inte är färsk?!\""

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for a Barbarian production site: Independent Fishing Hut
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:39 input:39
#: standard
msgctxt "barbarians_building"
msgid ""
"Frequent response of a Barbarian fisherman,<br>often followed by an "
"enjoyable brawl"
msgstr ""
"Vanligt svar från en barbarisk fiskare,<br>ofta följt av ett trevligt "
"slagsmål"

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:40
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:61 input:40
#: input:61 standard
msgid "Fishes on the coast near the fisher’s hut."
msgstr "Fiskar vid kusten nära fiskarens stuga."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:41
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:62 input:41
#: input:62 standard
msgid ""
"The independent fisher works slowly but is able to catch fish in places "
"where an ordinary fisher can't reach. Thanks to his larger reach, you can "
"get more fishes in total. It is useful only for open water."
msgstr ""
"Den oberoende fiskaren arbetar långsamt men kan fånga fisk på platser som en "
"vanlig fiskare inte når. Tack vare hans större räckvidd kan du fånga fler "
"fiskar totalt. Den är endast användbar på öppet vatten."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Empire production site: Independent Fishing Hut, part 1
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:44
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:65 input:44
#: input:65 standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid "The fisher needs %1$s on average to catch one fish."
msgstr "Fiskaren behöver i genomsnitt %1$s för att fånga en fisk."

#. TRANSLATORS: Performance helptext for an Empire production site: Independent Fishing Hut, part 2
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:46
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:67 input:46
#: input:67 standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid "In case of slopes or obstacles in the way, the time is increased."
msgstr "Vid lutningar eller hinder på vägen ökar tiden."

#. TRANSLATORS: DO NOT TRANSLATE, but you may transliterate into non-latin fonts.
#. Classical Latin quote meaning:
#. "Make haste slowly."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:54 input:54
#: standard
msgid "Festina lente."
msgstr "Festina lente."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Empire production site: Independent Fishing Hut
#. Translation for the classical Latin quote:
#. "Festina lente."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:58 input:58
#: standard
msgid "Make haste slowly."
msgstr "Skynda långsamt."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Empire production site: Independent Fishing Hut
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:60 input:60
#: standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid "Fisherman’s secret to catch more fishes"
msgstr "Fiskarens hemlighet för att fånga fler fiskar"

#. TRANSLATORS: DO NOT TRANSLATE, but you may transliterate into non-latin fonts.
#. Classical Latin quote meaning:
#. optional translation: "Let us improve life through science and art."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:77 input:77
#: standard
msgid "Inventas vitam iuvat excoluisse per artes."
msgstr "Inventas vitam iuvat excoluisse per artes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Empire production site: Advanced Stonemason's House
#. Translation for the classical Latin quote:
#. "Inventas vitam iuvat excoluisse per artes."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:81 input:81
#: standard
msgid "An innovative lifestyle helps to cultivate through art."
msgstr "En innovativ livsstil bidrar till att odla genom konst."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Empire production site: Advanced Stonemason's House
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:83 input:83
#: standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid "Motto of the Stonemasons’ Guild"
msgstr "Mottot för stenhuggarnas skrå"

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:84 input:84
#: standard
msgid "Carves marble columns out of marble."
msgstr "Hugger marmorpelare ur marmor."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:85 input:85
#: standard
msgid ""
"Advanced stonemason's house needs less marble to produce one marble column. "
"To produce one bulk of 3 columns, 4 pieces of marble are needed."
msgstr ""
"Avancerade stenhuggares hus behöver mindre marmor för att producera en "
"marmorpelare. För att producera en sändning med 3 pelare behövs 4 stycken "
"marmor."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:86 input:86
#: standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid "The stonemason needs %1% on average to carve one marble column."
msgstr "Stenhuggaren behöver i genomsnitt %1% för att hugga en marmorpelare."

#. TRANSLATORS: DO NOT TRANSLATE, but you may transliterate into non-latin fonts.
#. Classical Latin quote meaning:
#. "Eggs today are better than chickens tomorrow."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:94 input:94
#: standard
msgid "Ad praesens ova cras pullis sunt meliora."
msgstr "Ad praesens ova cras pullis sunt meliora."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Empire production site: Small Farm
#. Translation for the adapted classical Latin quote:
#. "Ad praesens ova cras pullis sunt meliora."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:98 input:98
#: standard
msgid "Eggs today are better than chickens tomorrow."
msgstr "Ägg idag är bättre än kycklingar imorgon."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Empire production site: Small Farm
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:100 input:100
#: standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid ""
"An impatient farmer considers building a small farm while sitting in a "
"warehouse during marble shortage"
msgstr ""
"En otålig bonde överväger att bygga en liten gård medan han sitter i en "
"lagerbyggnad under marmorbristen"

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:101 input:101
#: standard
msgid "Sows and harvests wheat."
msgstr "Sår och skördar vete."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:102 input:102
#: standard
msgid ""
"Production of two small farms is approximately equal to production of one "
"normal farm."
msgstr ""
"Produktionen från två små gårdar motsvarar ungefär produktionen från en "
"normal gård."

#. TRANSLATORS: DO NOT TRANSLATE, but you may transliterate into non-latin fonts.
#. Classical Latin quote meaning:
#. "Work conquers all things."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:110 input:110
#: standard
msgid "Labor omnia vincit."
msgstr "Arbetet övervinner allt."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for an Empire production site: Small Mill
#. Translation for the classical Latin quote:
#. "Labor omnia vincit."
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:114 input:114
#: standard
msgid "Work conquers all things."
msgstr "Arbetet övervinner allt."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore author helptext for an Empire production site: Small Mill
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:116 input:116
#: standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid ""
"A miller answering question whether his job wouldn’t be easier if he had a "
"better mill"
msgstr ""
"En mjölnare svarar på frågan om hans jobb inte skulle vara lättare om han "
"hade en bättre kvarn"

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:117 input:117
#: standard
msgid "Grinds wheat to produce flour."
msgstr "Maler vete för att producera mjöl."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:118 input:118
#: standard
msgctxt "empire_building"
msgid "The miller needs %1% on average to grind wheat into a sack of flour."
msgstr "Mjölaren behöver i genomsnitt %1% för att mala vete till en säck mjöl."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:163 input:163
#: standard
msgctxt "barbarians_building"
msgid ""
"‘Fine cloth and jewelry mean nothing to a true Barbarian.<br>But a noble "
"sail in the wind will please his eyes.’"
msgstr ""
"\"Fina kläder och smycken betyder ingenting för en sann barbar.<br>Men ett "
"ädelt segel i vinden gläder hans ögon.”"

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:165 input:165
#: standard
msgctxt "barbarians_building"
msgid ""
"Khantarakh, ‘The Modern Barbarian Economy’,<br>9ᵗʰ cowhide ‘Seafaring and "
"Conquest’"
msgstr ""
"Khantarakh, ”Den moderna barbariska ekonomin”,<br>9ᵗʰ cowhide ”Sjöfart och "
"erövring”"

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:166 input:166
#: standard
msgid "Weaves cloth out of reed."
msgstr "Vävt tyg av vass."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:167 input:167
#: standard
msgid "This building operates as an ordinary weaving mill only 20% slower."
msgstr "Denna byggnad fungerar som en vanlig vävfabrik endast 20% slägre."

#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:168 input:168
#: standard
msgctxt "barbarians_building"
msgid "The weaver needs %1% on average to weave reed into a piece of cloth."
msgstr "Vävaren behöver i genomsnitt %1% för att väva vass till ett tygstycke."

#. TRANSLATORS: Lore helptext for a Barbarian production site: Advanced Smelting Works
#: addons/barbarians_empire_economy_upgrade.wad/postload.lua:202 input:202
#: standard
msgctxt "barbarians_building"
msgid ""
"‘From inferior looking rubble they form shiny gold and gleaming iron.<br>The "
"smelters are real magicians among our craftsmen.’"
msgstr ""
"”Från grovskrot skapar de glänsande guld och skinande järn.<br>Smältarna är "
